CREATE TABLE dbo.Pais
	(
	CodPais INT NOT NULL,
	NomPais VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Pais PRIMARY KEY (CodPais)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Estado
	(
	CodPais   INT NOT NULL,
	CodEstado INT NOT NULL,
	NomEstado VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Estado PRIMARY KEY (CodPais,CodEstado),
	CONSTRAINT FK_Estado_Pais FOREIGN KEY (CodPais) REFERENCES dbo.Pais (CodPais)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Cidade
	(
	CodPais   INT NOT NULL,
	CodEstado INT NOT NULL,
	CodCidade INT NOT NULL,
	NomCidade VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Cidade PRIMARY KEY (CodPais,CodEstado,CodCidade),
	CONSTRAINT FK_Cidade_Estado FOREIGN KEY (CodPais,CodEstado) REFERENCES dbo.Estado (CodPais,CodEstado)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.QtdFuncionario
	(
	CodQtdFun INT NOT NULL,
	DesQtdFun VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_QtdFuncionario PRIMARY KEY (CodQtdFun)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Cargo
	(
	CodCargo INT NOT NULL,
	DesCargo VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Cargo PRIMARY KEY (CodCargo)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Empresa
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	NomEmpres VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	Telefone  BIGINT NULL,
	CodCNPJ   BIGINT NULL,
	AnoFundac INT NULL,
	TipEmpres VARCHAR (8) NULL,
	Matriz    BIT NULL,
	NomRespon VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	EmaRespon VARCHAR (200) NULL,
	TelRespon BIGINT NULL,
	CodCarRes INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Empresa PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres),
	CONSTRAINT FK_Empresa_Cargo FOREIGN KEY (CodCarRes) REFERENCES dbo.Cargo (CodCargo)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.HistLocalidade
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CodPais   INT NULL,
	CodEstado INT NULL,
	CodCidade INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_HistLocalidade PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistLocalidade_Cidade FOREIGN KEY (CodPais,CodEstado,CodCidade) REFERENCES dbo.Cidade (CodPais,CodEstado,CodCidade),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistLocalidade_Empresa FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres) REFERENCES dbo.Empresa (CodEmpres)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.HistQtdFunc
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CodQtdFun INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_HistQtdFunc PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistQtdFunc_QtdFunc FOREIGN KEY (CodQtdFun) REFERENCES dbo.QtdFuncionario (CodQtdFun),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistQtdFunc_Empresa FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres) REFERENCES dbo.Empresa (CodEmpres)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.ContatoEmp
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	CodContat INT NOT NULL,
	NomContat VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	EmaContat VARCHAR (200) NULL,
	TelContat BIGINT NULL,
	CodCarCnt INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_ContatoEmp PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres,CodContat),
	CONSTRAINT FK_ContatoEmp_Cargo FOREIGN KEY (CodCarCnt) REFERENCES dbo.Cargo (CodCargo),
	CONSTRAINT FK_ContatoEmp_Emp FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres) REFERENCES dbo.Empresa (CodEmpres)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.GrupoEmp
	(
	CodGrpEmp INT NOT NULL,
	NomGrpEmp VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_GrupoEmp PRIMARY KEY (CodGrpEmp)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Classificacao
	(
	CodClassi INT NOT NULL,
	DesClassi VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Classificacao PRIMARY KEY (CodClassi)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.HistClassi
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CodClassi INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_HistClassi PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistClassi_Classi FOREIGN KEY (CodClassi) REFERENCES dbo.Classificacao (CodClassi),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistClassi_Empresa FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres) REFERENCES dbo.Empresa (CodEmpres)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Faturamento
	(
	CodFatura INT NOT NULL,
	DesFatura VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Faturamento PRIMARY KEY (CodFatura)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.HistFatura
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CodFatura INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_HistFatura PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistFatura_Fatura FOREIGN KEY (CodFatura) REFERENCES dbo.Faturamento (CodFatura),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistFatura_Empresa FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres) REFERENCES dbo.Empresa (CodEmpres)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Segmento
	(
	CodSegmen INT NOT NULL,
	DesSegmen VARCHAR (200) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Segmento PRIMARY KEY (CodSegmen)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.AreaAtuacao
	(
	CodSegmen INT NOT NULL,
	CodAreAtu INT NOT NULL,
	NomAreAtu VARCHAR (200) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_AreaAtuacao PRIMARY KEY (CodSegmen,CodAreAtu),
	CONSTRAINT FK_AreaAtuacao_Seg FOREIGN KEY (CodSegmen) REFERENCES dbo.Segmento (CodSegmen)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.HistSegAreAtu
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CodSegmen INT NULL,
	CodAreAtu INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_HistSegAreAtu PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistSegAreAtu_AreAtu FOREIGN KEY (CodSegmen,CodAreAtu) REFERENCES dbo.AreaAtuacao (CodSegmen,CodAreAtu),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistSegAreAtu_Empresa FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres) REFERENCES dbo.Empresa (CodEmpres)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.HistGrupoEmp
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CodGrpEmp INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_HistGrupoEmp PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistGrupoEmp_Grp FOREIGN KEY (CodGrpEmp) REFERENCES dbo.GrupoEmp (CodGrpEmp),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistGrupoEmp_Emp FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres) REFERENCES dbo.Empresa (CodEmpres)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Imagem
	(
	CodImagem INT NOT NULL,
	DesImagem VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	Imagem    IMAGE NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Imagem PRIMARY KEY (CodImagem)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Processo
	(
	CodProces INT NOT NULL,
	DesProces VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CodImagem INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Processo PRIMARY KEY (CodProces),
	CONSTRAINT FK_Processo_Imagem FOREIGN KEY (CodImagem) REFERENCES dbo.Imagem (CodImagem)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.ProEmpAux
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	CodProces INT NOT NULL,
	Versao    INT NOT NULL,
	DataFinal SMALLDATETIME NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__ProEmpAu__F34220E1B186789C PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres,CodProces,Versao),
	CONSTRAINT FK_ProEmpAux_Proces FOREIGN KEY (CodProces) REFERENCES dbo.Processo (CodProces),
	CONSTRAINT FK_ProEmpAux_Empres FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres) REFERENCES dbo.Empresa (CodEmpres)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.SegmenProces
	(
	CodSegmen INT NOT NULL,
	CodProces INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__SegmenPr__11F3DD07D8913B49 PRIMARY KEY (CodSegmen,CodProces,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	CONSTRAINT FK_SegmenProces_Segmen FOREIGN KEY (CodSegmen) REFERENCES dbo.Segmento (CodSegmen),
	CONSTRAINT FK_SegmenProces_Proces FOREIGN KEY (CodProces) REFERENCES dbo.Processo (CodProces)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Pergunta
	(
	CodPergun INT NOT NULL,

	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.PergSegPro
	(
	CodSegmen INT NOT NULL,
	CodProces INT NOT NULL,
	CodPergun INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	Peso      FLOAT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__PergSegP__43C2829EE5B429FB PRIMARY KEY (CodSegmen,CodProces,CodPergun,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodPergun) REFERENCES dbo.Pergunta (CodPergun),
	CONSTRAINT FK_PergSegPro_Segmen FOREIGN KEY (CodSegmen) REFERENCES dbo.Segmento (CodSegmen),
	CONSTRAINT FK_PergSegPro_Proces FOREIGN KEY (CodProces) REFERENCES dbo.Processo (CodProces)
	)
GO

	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.RiscoPergunta
	(
	CodPergun INT NOT NULL,
	CodRisco  INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__RiscoPer__DD477BAF6D6C97E4 PRIMARY KEY (CodPergun,CodRisco,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodPergun) REFERENCES dbo.Pergunta (CodPergun),
	CONSTRAINT FK_RiscoPergunta_Pergun FOREIGN KEY (CodPergun) REFERENCES dbo.Pergunta (CodPergun),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodRisco) REFERENCES dbo.Risco (CodRisco),
	CONSTRAINT FK_RiscoPergunta_Risco FOREIGN KEY (CodRisco) REFERENCES dbo.Risco (CodRisco)
	)
GO


CREATE TABLE dbo.PerguntaProcesso
	(
	CodProces INT NOT NULL,
	CodPergun INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__Pergunta__95698D02A65505CA PRIMARY KEY (CodProces,CodPergun,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodPergun) REFERENCES dbo.Pergunta (CodPergun),
	CONSTRAINT FK_PerguntaProcesso_Pergun FOREIGN KEY (CodPergun) REFERENCES dbo.Pergunta (CodPergun),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodProces) REFERENCES dbo.Processo (CodProces),
	CONSTRAINT FK_PerguntaProcesso_Proces FOREIGN KEY (CodProces) REFERENCES dbo.Processo (CodProces)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Assunto
	(
	CodAssunt INT NOT NULL,
	DesAssunt VARCHAR (600) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Assunto PRIMARY KEY (CodAssunt)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Categoria
	(
	CodCatego INT NOT NULL,
	DesCatego VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Categoria PRIMARY KEY (CodCatego)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.GrpResposta
	(
	CodGrpRes INT NOT NULL,
	NomGrpRes VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_GrpResposta PRIMARY KEY (CodGrpRes)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Resposta
	(
	CodRespos INT NOT NULL,
	DesRespos VARCHAR (600) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__Resposta__C6CC192995806AE6 PRIMARY KEY (CodRespos)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.Usuario
	(
	CodUsuari INT NOT NULL,
	NomUsuari VARCHAR (150) NULL,
	EmaUsuari VARCHAR (200) NULL,
	PwdUsuari VARCHAR (250) NULL,
	PerfilUsu CHAR (1) NULL,
	DataBloqu VARCHAR (20) NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK_Usuario PRIMARY KEY (CodUsuari)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.HistGrpRes
	(
	CodGrpRes INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	TipoRespo INT NOT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__HistGrpR__37EC7893E902EF86 PRIMARY KEY (CodGrpRes,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodGrpRes) REFERENCES dbo.GrpResposta (CodGrpRes),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistGrpRes_GrpResposta FOREIGN KEY (CodGrpRes) REFERENCES dbo.GrpResposta (CodGrpRes)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.HistResposta
	(
	CodRespos INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	Percentua FLOAT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__HistResp__6F2A2E42FB7B976D PRIMARY KEY (CodRespos,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodRespos) REFERENCES dbo.Resposta (CodRespos),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistResposta_Respos FOREIGN KEY (CodRespos) REFERENCES dbo.Resposta (CodRespos)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.RespostaGrupo
	(
	CodGrupo  INT NOT NULL,
	CodRespos INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__Resposta__83CD1F538A7B5EF7 PRIMARY KEY (CodGrupo,CodRespos,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodGrupo) REFERENCES dbo.GrpResposta (CodGrpRes),
	CONSTRAINT FK_PK__RespostaGrupo_GrpResposta FOREIGN KEY (CodGrupo) REFERENCES dbo.GrpResposta (CodGrpRes),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodRespos) REFERENCES dbo.Resposta (CodRespos),
	CONSTRAINT FK_PK__RespostaGrupo_Resposta FOREIGN KEY (CodRespos) REFERENCES dbo.Resposta (CodRespos)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.HistPergunta
	(
	CodPergun INT NOT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	CodAssunt INT NULL,
	CodCatego INT NULL,
	CodGrpRes INT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__HistPerg__AF3CEFE950FAADF0 PRIMARY KEY (CodPergun,DataAlter,HoraAlter),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistPergunta_Pergunta FOREIGN KEY (CodPergun) REFERENCES dbo.Pergunta (CodPergun),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodCatego) REFERENCES dbo.Categoria (CodCatego),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistPergunta_Categoria FOREIGN KEY (CodCatego) REFERENCES dbo.Categoria (CodCatego),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodAssunt) REFERENCES dbo.Assunto (CodAssunt),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistPergunta_Assun FOREIGN KEY (CodAssunt) REFERENCES dbo.Assunto (CodAssunt),
	FOREIGN KEY (CodGrpRes) REFERENCES dbo.GrpResposta (CodGrpRes),
	CONSTRAINT FK_HistPergunta_GrpResposta FOREIGN KEY (CodGrpRes) REFERENCES dbo.GrpResposta (CodGrpRes)
	)
GO

CREATE TABLE dbo.ProcessoEmp
	(
	CodEmpres INT NOT NULL,
	CodProces INT NOT NULL,
	CodPergun INT NOT NULL,
	CodGrpRes INT NOT NULL,
	CodRespos INT NOT NULL,
	Nota      INT NULL,
	DataAlter SMALLDATETIME NOT NULL,
	HoraAlter INT NOT NULL,
	Versao    INT NOT NULL,
	DataFinal SMALLDATETIME NULL,
	CONSTRAINT PK__Processo__6B46B83DE9348D95 PRIMARY KEY (CodEmpres,CodProces,Versao,CodPergun,DataAlter,HoraAlter,CodGrpRes,CodRespos),
	CONSTRAINT FK_ProcessoEmp_Pergun FOREIGN KEY (CodPergun) REFERENCES dbo.Pergunta (CodPergun),
	CONSTRAINT FK_ProcessoEmp_GrpRes FOREIGN KEY (CodGrpRes) REFERENCES dbo.GrpResposta (CodGrpRes),
	CONSTRAINT FK_ProcessoEmp_Respos FOREIGN KEY (CodRespos) REFERENCES dbo.Resposta (CodRespos),
	CONSTRAINT FK_ProcessoEmp_Empres FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres) REFERENCES dbo.Empresa (CodEmpres),
	CONSTRAINT FK_ProcessoEmp_ProEmpAux FOREIGN KEY (CodEmpres,CodProces,Versao) REFERENCES dbo.ProEmpAux (CodEmpres,CodProces,Versao)
	)
GO
